			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Go to the Colony using the debugbook:&#xD;&#xA;- If you come through the main entrance, walk into the main corridor&#xD;&#xA;- If you come through the Necromancer's Room, walk to the main entrance&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- To trigger Wyll's nodes:&#xD;&#xA;Set HAV_Florrick_Event_WyllPresent_5763b529-e86f-7674-c385-5cfedf4ce556 or TWN_Wyll_State_MizorasCaptureWyllPresent_95c16d66-905f-ca29-f4ec-634a363d0e80&#xD;&#xA;and enter the triggers as Wyll" />
