			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="PAD discussing the Colony, how eerie it is, and reflecting on the (similar) nautiloid at the beginning of the game.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Started through COL_Entrance_VB&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;For Wyll: discussing either his mission to save his father or Mizora.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;" />
